/>\n<br />\n答案就係課埋壹週刊（每月$30 ／每年$288），保守估計而家有課壹週刊既可能連蘋果用戶1/10都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然對壹週刊d 娛樂新聞冇興趣，但係佢既時事專題都值得睇，而且有好多高質專訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有10萬人月課壹週刊，蘋果每個月就多300萬現金流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果一半蘋果用戶訂壹週刊，仲可能抵銷到之前用戶退訂既影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已課蘋果又想出多分力幫肥佬黎，立即課金壹週刊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/lC67NoYyJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FlC67NoYyJY&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=4f1f4a6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/lC67NoYyJY</a><br />\nAndroid：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.com.nextmedia.magazine.nextmediaplus&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dhk.com.nextmedia.magazine.nextmediaplus%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=2edcbef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.com.nextmedia.magazine.nextmediaplus&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\nios：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%A3%B9%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8A/id722696868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E5%25A3%25B9%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%2588%258A%2Fid722696868&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=75611768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%A3%B9%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8A/id722696868</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/sZ5xwcC.png\" />"}}